92
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:01,000
Tohle je hrob pana 
a paní Amamiyových?

93
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:04,200
Jo.

94
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:05,550
Kdo seš?

95
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:19,800
