96
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:21,050
Rodiče?

97
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:31,700
Divný.

98
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:33,800
Dneska je tu nějak rušno.

99
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,350
Jo no.

100
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,950
Naši by měli radost.

101
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:41,650
No, omlouvám se za potíže,

102
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:44,150
