115
00:21:57,100 --> 00:21:57,950
Ale...

116
00:21:58,030 --> 00:21:59,100
Jenom by ses 
nám pletla do cesty.

117
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:06,250
Počkej,

118
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:07,550
