119
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:13,850
Tady.

120
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:17,050
Tak co? Je po všem.

121
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:19,750
Co je?

122
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,900
Víte, kdo to byl?

123
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:25,700
Ne.

124
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:27,450
