125
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:28,600
Debilové?

126
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:30,500
Co to sakra?

127
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:31,600
To poděkování si domyslím.

128
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,650
Vypadá to, že jsou z Kuryu.

129
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,300
Kamizono Group.

130
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:43,600
Kamizono?

131
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:49,000
